# Mosquitto Password File Example
#
# To create a password file:
# 1. Copy this file to 'passwd' (remove .example extension)
# 2. Run: docker exec vandaemon-mqtt mosquitto_passwd -c /mosquitto/config/passwd username
# 3. Enter password when prompted
# 4. Uncomment password_file line in mosquitto.conf
# 5. Set allow_anonymous to false
# 6. Restart MQTT broker: docker restart vandaemon-mqtt
#
# To add more users:
# docker exec vandaemon-mqtt mosquitto_passwd -b /mosquitto/config/passwd username password
#
# Example users (DO NOT use these passwords in production!):
# vandaemon:passwordhash
# leddimmer:passwordhash
